QuestData.Title: Keys To Victory
QuestData.Description:
The song... incomplete. Harmony is needed. Seek those who scry. Send them to serve the cycle.
Mawsworn hold the keys that bind. Take the keys, set them free.
QuestData.LogDescription: Free $1oa Automa Scryers from their cells.
QuestData.RewardText: The chorus gathers. Soon, our voices will merge.
